<!-- Page 2 -->
<section id="page2">
    <h2>R.A 10630 Overview</h2>
    <p>1. Purpose:

R.A. 10630 aims to strengthen the NIA, emphasizing the crucial role of efficient irrigation in agricultural development.

The law seeks to provide a sustainable and reliable water supply to farmers, ultimately improving crop yields and contributing to food security.

2. Key Provisions:

The law outlines provisions for the expansion, repair, and modernization of irrigation systems.

It promotes the optimal utilization of water resources, emphasizing responsible water management practices.

</p>
