<!-- Page 3 -->
<section id="page3">
    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <p>Irrigation System Modernization:

R.A. 10630 focuses on the modernization of irrigation systems, aiming to enhance their efficiency and effectiveness in providing water to agricultural lands.

National Irrigation Administration (NIA) Strengthening:

The law strengthens the NIA, empowering the agency to play a central role in the planning, implementation, and management of irrigation projects.

</p>
